description.narrative: 4.1.H More adolescent girls, mothers and newborns receive essential maternal and newborn care in health facilities through quality, afforda ble and effective MNCH services, which contributes to Child Health, Health Systems Strengthening, Maternal And Newborn Health. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Developing And Leveraging Resources And Partnerships, Evaluations, Research And Data, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: PCR 4 ACSD Fewer women die and women are better enabled to care for their children
